name: XTZ Opyum sandals
description: An iconic, instantly recognizable Parisian silhouette redefining the heel with the Opyum sandals. Replacing the traditional stiletto shape with «XTZ» sculptural monogram, this work injects modernist flair and a luxurious aura into the statement silhouette. Chic straps complete the design, bootstrapping ready to turn heads at your next crypto soirée! twitter.com/robertpavelart instagram.com/robertpavelart
